  06 Nov 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> scli-0.4.0-r1.ebuild,
  +files/scli-0.4.0-configure.patch, -files/scli-0.4.0-tinfo.patch:
  Fix building against =net-libs/gnet-2.0.8-r2 (bug #528378).

  16 Jul 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -scli-0.4.0.ebuild,
  scli-0.4.0-r1.ebuild, +files/scli-0.4.0-tinfo.patch:
  EAPI bump. Fix building against sys-libs/ncurses[tinfo]. New HOMEPAGE. Remove
  AR hack now that we run eautoreconf. Remove USE=debug as nothing uses
  HAVE_DMALLOC_H anyway.

  20 Nov 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> scli-0.4.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #441432

  10 Nov 2012; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> scli-0.4.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64-linux keyword

  10 Nov 2012; Sergey Popov <pinkbyte@gentoo.org> scli-0.4.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64, bug #441432

  24 Sep 2012; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -scli-0.2.12.ebuild,
  -files/scli-0.2.12-fix-configure.diff, -files/scli-0.2.12-gentoo.diff:
